label: SupplyChainTradeTransaction
comment: A group of supply chain trade line items, trade agreement, trade delivery and trade settlement details.

datatypeProperties.comment: The Uniform Resource Locator (URL) of the web location of the document for this supply chain trade transaction.

A code specifying a type of MDH health indication.
